<h3 id="applications-for-postgraduate">Applications for Postgraduate</h3>
<p>If you are interested in working with us as a Postgraduate student, please send me an email (gqliu1010@163.com). State briefly why you are interested and attach a CV, including information about the grades you had as an undergraduate. No need for a separate cover letter or certificates. <strong>Important</strong>: please insert <em>“Application Postgraduate”</em> in the subject line. If you are applying to a specific advertisement, note this in your email.</p>

<h3 id="bsc--master-students">Bsc / Master students</h3>
<p>If you are a undergraduate or a Master student looking for a project, contact me (or any group member) per email or stop by my office.</p>

<h3 id="visiting-students-and-scholars">Visiting students and scholars</h3>
<p>If you are a student or a scholar from other universities and interested in joining our group as a visiting student/scholar, please send me an email.</p>

